snippet.textDisplay:
As a native Virginian, I feel the need to note that Edgar was indeed from RICHMOND, not Baltimore...which is consistent with the story told in this video...he went to UVA...


ALSO anyone who works in healthcare and knows a little bit about medicine knows that people who struggle with alcohol and who go thru detoxification is not a pretty sight...that would explain his symptoms in the hospital and his death. What happened before he got to the hospital could be explained by the other theories, but to me it is not unusual at all the way he died from alcohol detoxification. Patients like that are at high risk of encephalopathy, delirium tremens/seizures, and death.

snippet.textDisplay:
For Postmortem: I believe the cooping theory is the best theory. Poe was pulled in to the polling place, gave him a drink, and realizing he got drunk real easily, manipulated Poe and made him vote multiple times. After voting, Poe may have wanted more liquor and probably got violent and thus knocked on the head and thrown out. This would explain why Poe was found outside a polling place and would also explain the supposed head trauma may have suffered. As for the raggedy clothes, I believe they were his regular clothes that got ragged up when he was drunk, after all, he was found in the gutter and who knows how long he was there for. It's likely he was lying there for the whole 5 days and no one ever noticed.

P.S. I feel like Ryan's reaction to the Baltimore Ravens fact was staged if not overly exaggerated.
